oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Morris Levy Job No. 36691
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Snow, Hank; Flatt, Lester; Scruggs, Earl; Wells, Kitty; Dudley, Dave;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1239) for an order placed by Morris Levy for 300 two color jumbos and 300 two color window cards for a performance by Hank Snow, Lester Flatt, Early Scruggs, Kitty Wells, and Dave Dudley at the Paramount Theatre in New York City, New York from April 30 to May 6. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
